{
  "stem": "6525.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somebody said to Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody said to Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we will go to working camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] People were sitting around and doing nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had for little kids-- they had kindergartens, nurseries.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you have to know that a scared people can do nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They don't have the energy even to survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you're scared of the future, of your life, then you don't have the energy to do anything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How long?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Five weeks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a person, and after him was named his factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was with us in the [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kalush ?] factory.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is a whole story about the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And nobody knows about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my mother wasn't very friendly with the rebbetzin before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't want to talk bad things about dead people, but she said that the rebbetzin is a snob.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she didn't-- but she wasn't a friend before with the rebbetzin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in the [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Kalush ?] factory, they were always talking very quietly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody should hear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had always conversations.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And what I hear from this conversation, the rebbetzin was complaining that her husband sits in a corner, depressed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He's not eating.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He's not moving around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He's just fasting and praying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she was very concerned about him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she needed help, but she didn't want to go to nobody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my mother find out when they were taken from the house, they didn't have anything with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I took over for them two sheets and two towels.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But this was a big secret.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Nobody's not supposed to know that the rabbi is that bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when we went into the cattle cars, the rabbi was in the same car.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
